2) cs.LG - The paper involves the use of machine learning techniques to learn a heuristic-like policy for solving the 3D flexible bin packing problem. 
3) cs.CV - The paper involves the packing of cuboid-shaped items into a bin, which could be seen as a computer vision problem. 
4) cs.DS - The paper involves the optimization of packing items into a bin, which could be seen as a data structure problem. 
5) cs.RO - The paper involves the optimization of packing items into a bin, which could be seen as a robotics problem.
